column5: Hello  Just picked up an Eskimo quickfish 70"x70" insulated pop up  Reg $499 for $299  Canadian tire  On sale till the 15th or 16th  Now I can take my son (3.5yrs old) out in comfort
Great price Mike,they have had some really good deals on a lot of stuff this past few weeks.!!

Sorry to burst your bubble but Lebarons has it regular price for $259.94. Maybe you can price match? I have found on some items that CT's sale prices are other retailer's regular prices. Great price, though, if Lebarons is too far away.  Jon
Jon, the one on sale at CT is the QF3i which is the insulated model..... the one at LeBaron is the QF3 uninsulated model, hence the much lower price.  Burt
How is this hut? Any personal experience with this one?
Set it up in the living room...  It's aweful nice...  Gunna take  my boy out to test it Saturday...  I'll give a review
Burt and Mike:  My apologies on the error and thanks for the clarification.  Jon
What a deal guys,that's one to look at for that price!
